    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-809e-bfb2-ec2da3688753",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The effectiveness of collaboration in large courses such as MOOCs is under-researched. MOOCs rarely require the formation of groups or, even if they allow it, educators often can not put criteria for formation. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-809e-bfb2-ec2da3688753",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
          "page_id": "4932f78c-6d96-415c-9ae5-f266f9260071"
        },
        "created_time": "2025-02-03T22:59:00.000Z",
        "last_edited_time": "2025-02-03T23:07:00.000Z",
        "created_by": {
